                <salute>farewell my beloved sons<ptr target="uva.00365_n2"/></salute>
            </opener>
            
            <p>farewell i have lived beyond
                all comfort in this world dont
                mourn for me my beloved
                sons and daughters farewel
                my dear beloved
                walter<ptr target="uva.00365_n3"/></p>
